  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK377">
<l>vakuttāṉ vakutta vakaiyallāṟ kōṭi</l>
<l>tokuttārkkut tuytta laritu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even those who gather together millions will only enjoy them, as it has been determined by the disposer (of all things).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
